  "detailed_description": "Imagine that there are plenty of gull. In the universe the game is located in, gulls just pop-up with each level-change.<br />\r\nYou, the player of the game, are supposed to get their numbers down by using advanced weaponry.<br />\r\nThe game can be sustained for unbounded periods of time. The goal of the game is to shoot gulls.<br />\r\nYou can shoot a lot, or you can shoot a few, it does not really matter. They keep re-spawning anyway with each level change.<br />\r\nThe game lacks any form of moral. It is an unfair struggle between you and those gulls.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYour weapons have been modified to accommodate arcade mode. That means no running out of bullets and thus no reloading.",
  "about_the_game": "Imagine that there are plenty of gull. In the universe the game is located in, gulls just pop-up with each level-change.<br />\r\nYou, the player of the game, are supposed to get their numbers down by using advanced weaponry.<br />\r\nThe game can be sustained for unbounded periods of time. The goal of the game is to shoot gulls.<br />\r\nYou can shoot a lot, or you can shoot a few, it does not really matter. They keep re-spawning anyway with each level change.<br />\r\nThe game lacks any form of moral. It is an unfair struggle between you and those gulls.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYour weapons have been modified to accommodate arcade mode. That means no running out of bullets and thus no reloading.",
